The mostutils script collection

Including:

 * Commands to set the volume e.g. mute and ACPI scripts

 * The Trim commands

 * Some commands equivalent to Perl moduls

 * Some sed and AWK scripts

If a script can be written as a POSIX-shell script and only using
coreutils then it is a POSIX-shell script elsewise it is a Perl script.
But if sed or AWK is the better/faster tool then it is a sed or AWK
script.

Und dennoch, es sollte versucht werden, soviel als möglich in Perl zu schreiben.
